                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Stack Critical Strike Chance aggressively.</strong>
                    <p>Heartseeker's damage scales entirely off crits. Aim for 50%+ crit chance minimum, preferably 60%+. Every piece of gear should have crit chance or crit damage.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Stay at maximum range for Aspect of Retribution.</strong>
                    <p>Distant enemies take bonus crit chance. Stay at the edge of your attack range to maintain this buff constantly for maximum damage output.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Maintain full Energy for Condemnation bonus.</strong>
